          </div>
          <div class='col-lg text-lg-end text-center experience-title'>
            September 2021 - Today
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col px-5'>
            <ul class='pt-lg-0 pt-3 text-lg-start text-center'>
              <li>
                <a
                  class='ffc-link'
                  href='https://www.freecodecamp.org/certification/ademine/responsive-web-design'
                  target='_blank'
                >Responsive Web Design
                  <img src='/images/fcc_secondary_small.svg' alt='' /></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  class='ffc-link'
                  href='https://www.freecodecamp.org/certification/ademine/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures'
