                  <img src='/images/fcc_secondary_small.svg' alt='' /></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  class='ffc-link'
                  href='https://www.freecodecamp.org/certification/ademine/front-end-development-libraries'
                  target='_blank'
                >Front End Development Libraries
                  <img src='/images/fcc_secondary_small.svg' alt='' /></a>
              </li>
              <li>
                <a
                  class='ffc-link'
                  href='https://www.freecodecamp.org/certification/ademine/back-end-development-and-apis'
                  target='_blank'
                >Back End Development and APIs
                  <img src='/images/fcc_secondary_small.svg' alt='' /></a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Experience #2 -->
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-lg text-lg-start text-center pb-2 experience-title'>
            Technical Services Manager
          </div>
          <div class='col-lg text-lg-end text-center experience-title'>
            April 2021 - August 2021
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col px-5'>
            <ul class='pt-lg-0 pt-3 text-lg-start text-center'>
              <li>Planning preventive maintenance of installations.</li>
              <li>Leading a team of 8 technicians.</li>
              <li>Management of external contractors for major works.</li>
              <li>
                Planning and implementation of maintenance and optimization
                projects.
              </li>
              <li>
                Development of a culture focused on operational technologies.
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Experience #2 -->
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col-lg text-lg-start text-center pb-2 experience-title'>
            Technical Services Manager
          </div>
          <div class='col-lg text-lg-end text-center experience-title'>
            June 2019 - March 2021
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col px-5'>
            <ul class='pt-lg-0 pt-3 text-lg-start text-center'>
              <li>
                Detail Engineering (Technical drawings and I/O definition).
              </li>
              <li>Functional description of complex automated systems.</li>
              <li>Ladder programming of automated systems.</li>
              <li>Supervision of electrical construction and dismantling.</li>
              <li>Commissioning and testing of complex automated systems.</li>
              <li>Maintaining relationships with customers.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact me section -->
    <div
      class='container-fluid content-section border-top border-dark px-5'
      id='contact'
    >
      <div class='row'>
        <!-- Section Title -->

        <div class='row'>
          <div class='row mb-5'>
            <div class='col text-center section-title'>#contact</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class='row'>
          {{msg}}
        </div>
        <!-- Contact Form -->
        <form action='/send' method='post' id='contact-form' class='row'>
          <!-- Email and Subject -->
          <div class='col-md-6 mb-3'>
            <input
              type='email'
              class='form-control'
              name='email'
              placeholder='email'
            />
          </div>
          <div class='col-md-6 mb-3'>
            <input
              type='text'
              class='form-control'
              name='subject'
              placeholder='subject'
            />
          </div>
          <!-- Message -->
          <div class='col-12 mb-3'>
            <textarea
              class='form-control'
              name='message'
              rows='3'
              placeholder='message'
            ></textarea>
          </div>
          <div class='col-12 text-end'>
            <button type='submit' class='btn btn-dark'>send</button>
          </div>
          <div class='col-12 text-center'></div>
        </form>
        <div class='row'>
          <div class='col text-center'>
            <a
              href='https://www.linkedin.com/in/gdesrosiers
            '
              target='_blank'
            ><img src='/images/linkedin.svg' alt='linkedin icon' /></a>
            <a href='https://www.freecodecamp.org/ademine' target='_blank'><img
                src='/images/fcc_secondary_small.svg'
                alt='freecodecamp icon'
              /></a>
            <a href='https://github.com/mesieu' target='_blank'><img
                src='/images/github.svg'
                alt='github icon'
              /></a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

